<br />
<br />Once I can find time (it's not easy with a very young child)  I will try to use your new code and test it back on my dev-cart to see how much different it is.  If you don't mind, instead of making "a new branch",I would like to insert in your project a few extra line so I can compile easily for MMC3 CHR-RAM and you could merge it after.  I guess it could be made so it can be compiled for a NROM or MMC3 very easily.</div>

